description	"Mandalore the Preserver

Class: Clone Trooper.
Tactical Summary:
A tanky commander with a heavy repeater, quickthrow grenades and a long-reaching vibro-sword. 

Default Weaponry:
Vibro-Sword
- Can use Yellow and Red styles
- Melee weapon based on Lightsaber
- Deals reduced damage
- Cannot block blaster fire
- Can block lightsabers

Default Attributes:
-Dexterity (1)
-Ammo (3)
-Rally

Customization Options:

-Repeating Blaster: Clone Trooper Rifle (1/2/3)
-Heavy Blobs: Clone Trooper Heavy Blobs (+2 per level)
-Health: Extra HP (110,125,140)
-Healing: Hero Class Healing
-Stamina: Clone/Arc Stamina
-Blast Armor: Explosives and Melee Damage resistance
-Cortosis: Lightsaber resistance
-Armor: Extra Armor (75,90,115)
-Beskar: Mandalorian Class Beskar Armor
-Vibro-Sword Defense: Defense 1 to block sabers/melee weapons
-Improved Melee (+AP): Increased AP multiplier (1.0/1.1/1.2)


Canderous Ordo, later known as Mandalore the Preserver, was a Mandalorian of Clan Ordo who fought in the Mandalorian Wars and earned significant glory and prestige with his bold tactics and leadership."